# ============================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES
# ============================================
# Files that SHOULD be committed:
# ✓ mvnw, mvnw.cmd (needed for Render)
# ✓ Dockerfile (needed for Render)
# ✓ docker-compose.yml (needed for local dev)
# ✓ render.yaml (optional, for infrastructure as code)
# ✓ vercel.json (needed for Vercel SPA routing)
# ✓ pom.xml (backend dependencies)
# ✓ package.json (frontend dependencies)
# ✓ src/ directories (your code!)
# ✓ README.md (project documentation)
#
# Files that should NEVER be committed:
# ✗ .env files (contain secrets)
# ✗ node_modules/ (reinstall with npm install)
# ✗ target/ (rebuild with mvn package)
# ✗ dist/ (rebuild with npm run build)
# ✗ *.log files (generated at runtime)
# ============================================

